Kar gay, gamin kuuk Ruwwin ta Buŋdi beriy-ak, ŋuur ko ele, galal, aapiy, subirraw, selliŋkaw, selliŋkaw, selliŋkaw, imaan,
Kar Iisa gay ƴalaaŋ di uŋda a ŋaa tale waa kaak diiriiga.
Minninko-aŋ, ya goy gem kaak gin ilim ho kaak gin pikirre, illa ŋaa gaare iŋ goyin̰ji kaak samaane ho iŋ dalullaw kadar ŋa gin ilim. Illa ŋaa gaare iŋ riy taat ŋa gingiyo kadar ŋa gina gamin iŋ dalullaw ho iŋ riy taat sellen̰.
Kar sultan kaawiiji ɗo gay riyor-ak aman: ‟ Ɗuunig asin̰ji iŋ pisin̰ji ho ɗuunoŋga ho accoŋ kara ɗo gondikor. Ɗo wer-ak, ŋuu eeyme saaŋco ho zulin̰co yaa min̰e dakina. "
Kar Iisa kaawiiji ɗo gem-ak aman: " Dak kaawenno bat ɗo waanna. Kar gay, ɓaa gaar zin̰ ɗo gay satkiner ho ber *satkin uudin taat gaanuun ka Muusa kaawtu. Paa kat, ŋuu ibine kadar ki cale "
Daarin̰co ɗiya aman: " Ŋa ŋaar ko Masi kaak Buŋ doɓtu. " Kar daarin̰ gay ɗiya aman: " Masi-ak yaa amile min Galile walla?
Hiyya, min ŋa pakirtu pa-ak, ŋa ɓaawtu wer kan̰ Mariyam atan̰ Yaaya kaak ŋu koliy oki Maark. Ɗo wer-ak, gee dakina n̰umtu ho ŋu salkiyaw.
Jeese roŋji ka Jeese, Jeese roŋji ka Obeed, Obeed roŋji ka Booz, Booz roŋji ka Salmoon, Salmoon roŋji ka Nasoon.
Ka seener, zi kaak yaa zooɗe-ak yaa jipte iŋ kaak zooɗaaɗo, ho kaak mataaɗo-ak yaa jipte iŋ kaak mate.
Kar ɗo wiktin taar-at, Iisa gay weƴa ka dariŋgildi. Maajirnay niiniig ho ŋu ɗiyiiji aman: " Gem kol tacco, kiŋ isgicinno ɗo bi ka amay-aŋku walla? "
Min ŋu obig Yaaya daŋaayne, Iisa uctu, ŋa ɓaawtu ɗo kiɗ ka Galile, ŋa gaariy Kabarre ta Gala taat asa min ɗo Buŋdi.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-aŋ, gem kol siŋtay, oboŋ aditko, asaan nu aamin iŋ Buŋ ho nu kaawiy kadar kaaw taat ŋa kaawiidu-an yaa kuuniye uudin taat ŋa kaawiidu-anta.
Asaan Buŋ, ŋaar Buŋɗo ka barjilindi, ŋaar Buŋ ka aapiyer. Ar kaak ɗo *Eglizna okin̰co kuuk gee ku Buŋdi n̰umgiyo,
Kar kuŋ gay iban kadar Iisa Masi as ɗo duniiner a ŋaa sooyin̰ zunuubinnite ku geemir. Ho ŋaar gay ginno zunuubinna tak-tak.
Gee dakina minninco ɗiytu aman: " Ŋa gin aariɗ ɗo kaay ho ŋa oliyaw. Maa di ku cokiyiiga? "
Nu kaawaajiŋ a ki tiyaaɗo kum, ki saaɗo maam ku *bin̰di ho ki ginno maan kaak yaa jage siŋjiŋ yaa jage min botol ta Buŋdi.
Iisa gay telkiiji aman: " Ki ooy a kii ooye muutu ɗo bi kanto walla? Ka seener nu kaawaajiŋ waraŋ, kokir boogaaɗo di, kii tatire dees subba a ki ibinginno. "
Ɗo wer-ak di, mic-at uctu ho ta teestu jaawe. Elginti yaa nece ar orok iŋ seer pa. Min maajirnay taliit pa-ak, ŋu ajbiytu tak-tak.
Gem kaak kaawa kaawin kuuk ta meen̰ji di-ak, ŋaar bariya ozile ka meen̰ji di. Kar ŋaar kaak bariya ozile ka ŋaar kaak tabirga-ak gay, ŋaar ka seener ho kaaw sa ginno iŋ ŋaara.
Iisa gay telkiico aman: " Maa di ku bariyiinu? Ku ibanno kadar illa naa goye ɗo wer kaak Tanni goyiyo walla? "
Nu taaƴiiciŋ-ak asaan wiktin taat nu ɓaayiy ɗo kiɗ ka Maseduwaan, nu taaƴiŋ ko goye ɗo geeger ka Epeez. Ansii ko, kiico ɗiye ɗo gee daarin̰ kuuk ɓilda gee iŋ kaawin ku pey.
Di ŋaar-ak gay, ibinoŋ tam kadar min gee ku Israyeel okin̰co, ka seener, Iisa kaak ku ɗooɗtu ka etor-aŋ ko, Buŋ diyig *Rabbine ho *Masi kaak ku ɗooɗtu. "
Simon Piyer iŋ *maajirin̰ce ka pey aaɗaaga ɗo Iisa. Maajirin̰ce-ak gay, mee satkiner ka tatko-ak ibingiy dakina. Ampaa ko, ŋa un̰jitu iŋ Iisa ɗo wer ka berel ka ger ka mee satkiner-aka.
Dakoŋ moyenno ɗo bi ka teendi wala ka seendi ho dakoŋ moyenno ɗo gamin-aŋku.
Ɗo wer-ak, agindaw ku gaanuundi iŋ Pariziyenna dapin̰tu aale. Ŋu teestu kaawe benannico maan kaak ŋuu gine ɗo Iisa.
Hiyya, Iisa indiig maajirnay kuuk orok iŋ seera aman: " Kuŋko oki raka ɗeete walla? "
Iisa ɗiytu aman: " Ɗak mena sooɗ di, ku talaanno pey, kar ba aar sooɗ di, kuun talindu. "
Gem kol siŋtay, ya ku taaɓiya iŋ ay taaɓine, pakiroŋ kadar taaɓin-at yaa ase iŋ galal okintiti.
Iisa gay telkiico aman: " Nun aariɗɗo. Nu bera horoomine ɗo Tanni, kar kuŋ gay karmiyginu.
Iisa gay telkiico aman: " Gee kuuk cokiyit gaaƴ-an, ŋu bal kaawe ɗo bi kanto, kar gay, ŋu kaaw a taa gaaye loko.
Ŋa osiiteŋ ko maan kaak kuuniy awalle. Ɗo wer-ak, ɗubil ka Buŋdi bayniiji ho ŋa kaawiiji aman: ‟ N̰aam gee ɗo geeger ka Jappa, ŋu ɓaayiy kole gem rakki siŋji Simon kaak ŋu koliy oki Piyer.
